							<text>
37 year old gentleman lives in bungalow with his wife, has recently had episode of Intermediate Care at home for mobility practice following a stroke. Today attended A&amp;E by own transport - had been unwell with chest infection, seen by GP and started on antibiotics - had  <content ID="a12"> fallen when getting out of the shower</content> (no fractures) and had also developed a whole body rash and wife was concerned. Medically fit, but referred to social services as <content ID="a13"> wife finding it hard to cope </content>in <content ID="a6">carer</content> role.
							</text>
